## 1. Single Supabase Client Boundary

**RULE:** All app code imports the Supabase client from `@/infrastructure/supabase`. Never import from `@/integrations/supabase/client` — that file is internal and auto-managed by Lovable.

```ts
// CORRECT
import { supabase } from '@/infrastructure/supabase';

// WRONG — never do this in app code
import { supabase } from '@/integrations/supabase/client';
```

The only file allowed to import from `@/integrations/supabase/client` is `src/infrastructure/supabase.ts` itself.

