## 2. Repository Pattern — DB Access Rules

**RULE:** All database reads and writes go through repository files under `src/features/*/repositories/`. No `supabase.from()` calls in pages, components, hooks, or services.

### Allowed exceptions in pages/components/hooks
- `supabase.storage.from(...)` — file uploads
- `supabase.rpc(...)` — aggregation RPCs (counts, member profiles)
- `supabase.channel(...)` / `supabase.removeChannel(...)` — realtime subscriptions
- `supabase.auth.*` — auth operations

