### When adding a new feature
1. Create `src/features/{domain}/repositories/{name}Repository.ts`
2. Import supabase from `@/infrastructure/supabase`
3. Add `createLogger` with structured logging on all write methods
4. If the write is sensitive (see Section 4), route it through an edge function via `callEdgeFunction`
5. Export the repository and use it from hooks/pages — never call Supabase directly

