## 6. Feature Module Structure

```
src/features/{domain}/
  ├── domain/
  │   └── types.ts          # Domain types/interfaces
  ├── repositories/
  │   └── {name}Repository.ts  # All DB access
  ├── services/
  │   └── {name}Service.ts     # Business logic (calls repos)
  └── index.ts              # Barrel exports
```

**Data flow:** Pages/Hooks → Services → Repositories → Supabase

Services must call repositories, not Supabase directly. The one known exception is `feedService.ts` which still does direct post/repost queries (slated for cleanup).

